Package org.jdesktop.jdic.browser

Interface Summary
WebBrowserListener The listener interface for receiving WebBrowser events.
 

Class Summary
WebBrowser A WebBrowser component represents a blank rectangular area of the screen onto which the application can display webpages or from which the application can trap events from the browser window.
WebBrowser.Status An inner class which is used for retrieving the WebBrowser's property, such as initialization status, back and forward status.
WebBrowserEvent A WebBrowser Event is dispatched by WebBrowser object to its listeners when one of the the defined events happens.
